TAMARA LANZA was born in Argentina, has lived in 5 countries all over the world and currently resides in sunny Los Angeles.  She thrives on the creative arts continually manifesting musical, visual arts and performances, creating original music in her home studio in Woodland Hills, CA.  She is currently very active in the Los Angeles music scene with multiple weekly Live performances as both, DJ and rock musician. Any given day or night you might find her performing at a nightclub, underground warehouse rave, desert oasis, music festival, or anywhere there is music.
